          "content": "\n                    <div class=\"mb-6\">\n                        <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-4\">AI Safety and Ethics</h3>\n                        <p class=\"mb-4\">As your AI safety instructor with 10 years of experience analyzing AI failures, I'll teach you how to build safe, ethical AI systems that benefit everyone.</p>\n                        \n                        <div class=\"bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-6\">\n                            <h4 class=\"font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2\">üéØ Learning Objectives</h4>\n                            <ul class=\"text-blue-800 space-y-1\">\n                                <li>‚Ä¢ Understand core AI safety principles</li>\n                                <li>‚Ä¢ Learn bias detection and mitigation techniques</li>\n                                <li>‚Ä¢ Master AI risk assessment frameworks</li>\n                                <li>‚Ä¢ Implement responsible AI governance</li>\n                            </ul>\n                        </div>\n                        \n                        <img src=\"/nist-ai-risk-framework.png\" alt=\"NIST AI Risk Management Framework\" class=\"w-full max-h-96 object-contain mx-auto mb-6 rounded-lg shadow-md\" />\n                        \n                        <h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3\">AI Risk Assessment Matrix</h4>\n                        <div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\">\n                            <table class=\"min-w-full bg-white border border-gray-200\">\n                                <thead class=\"bg-orange-500 text-white\">\n                                    <tr>\n                                        <th class=\"px-4 py-3 text-left\">Risk Category</th>\n                                        <th class=\"px-4 py-3 text-left\">Impact Level</th>\n                                        <th class=\"px-4 py-3 text-left\">Mitigation Strategy</th>\n                                        <th class=\"px-4 py-3 text-left\">Monitoring Method</th>\n                                    </tr>\n                                </thead>\n                                <tbody class=\"divide-y divide-gray-200\">\n                                    <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50\">\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">Algorithmic Bias</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">üî•üî•üî• High</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Diverse training data, Fairness metrics</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Regular bias audits</td>\n                                    </tr>\n                                    <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50\">\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">Privacy Violation</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">üî•üî•üî• High</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Data minimization, Encryption</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Privacy impact assessments</td>\n                                    </tr>\n                                    <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50\">\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">Model Drift</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">üî•üî• Medium</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Continuous monitoring, Retraining</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Performance metrics tracking</td>\n                                    </tr>\n                                    <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50\">\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">Adversarial Attacks</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">üî•üî• Medium</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Robust training, Input validation</td>\n                                        <td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Anomaly detection</td>\n                                    </tr>\n                                </tbody>\n                            </table>\n                        </div>\n                        \n                        <div class=\"bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-4\">\n                            <h4 class=\"font-semibold text-red-900 mb-2\">üö® Critical Safety Reminder</h4>\n                            <p class=\"text-red-800\">AI safety isn't a one-time check‚Äîit's an ongoing process. The most dangerous AI systems are those that work perfectly in testing but fail catastrophically in production.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    "
